            <h3>Benefits of Signing Up</h3>
            <h5>mart87.com gets you best search results based on your past purchases</h5>
              
              <ul>
                <li>Access all your past purchases under a single view along with dates and amounts to easily go back in time and re-order</li>

                <li>Earn credit/saving points every time you shop and even pay or round off your totals using your mart87 point</li>

                <li>Save frequently bought items into lists and enjoy a faster shopping experience</li>

                  <li>mart87.com remembers your addresses, preferred time slots and payment methods speeding up your checkout process</li>


              </ul>


